user.biography:
Small family-owned toy shop. 
🍽 Every purchase helps provide meals for kids in need
📦 Flat-rate US shipping: $3.50
🌴 Based in Rancho Mission Viejo, CA

node.text: Curious George is one of my son’s all-time favorite shows and these two definitely remind me of George and Hundley. So I thought it would be fun to play a trivia game. Head over to our stories to play and get a $20 shop credit!
